  stimulus_text = 'The United States is a vast country, and its diverse population makes it a melting pot of cultures. However, the country’s vast size and diverse population can also make it difficult to understand the nuances of the various cultures that exist within its borders. The most important thing to remember when interacting with people from different cultures is to be respectful and open-minded. What is the most likely reason why the writer chooses to use the phrase "melting pot"?',
